---
title: Double Honey-Glazed Haloumi Couscous with Roast Veggies & Basil Pesto
description: Indulge your taste buds with a tantalizing dish of honey-glazed haloumi nestled atop a bed of fluffy couscous and perfectly roasted
veggies. The vibrant flavors are elevated with the addition of basil pesto, creating a harmonious and satisfying culinary experience.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/659f93451ee0609964a9bb5c-b7835f6f.jpeg
